content:
Elevate Scheduler Efficiency With an Improved User Interface

Help schedulers view related visits and group visits directly from the patient's record page with the updated Home Health Visit component. With active links in the Related Visit and Related Group columns, schedulers can save time, access accurate details, and reduce repetitive navigation.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise and Unlimited editions with the Health Cloud and the Home Health add-on licenses.

Who: This feature is available to users with the Manage Home Health permission set license.

How: In the Lightning App Builder, place the Home Health Visits lightning component on the Person Account record page.
title: Elevate Scheduler Efficiency with Improved UI in Salesforce
